rows.label: qst003103_msg0001
rows.name:
What? You're gonna lend
us a hand, are you?

rows.label: qst003103_msg0003
rows.name:
We're short of meat-based meals
at this distribution center.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0004
rows.name:
Reckon you could get a few meaty
dishes made up and bring 'em here?

rows.label: qst003103_msg0005
rows.name:
Thanks for the help. Things are
looking a little brighter for us now.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0006
rows.name:
We've been pretty busy since all
these Acedian refugees showed up.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0007
rows.name:
Sometimes I think it'd be easier
if we just sent 'em back.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0008
rows.name:
We're struggling to feed
our own people here.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0009
rows.name:
People start to get a bit
edgy when they see us doling
out food to these Acedians.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0010
rows.name:
To be honest, they've caused
quite a bit of trouble recently.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0011
rows.name:
Don't get me wrong, I've got a
lot of sympathy for these
refugees, after what happened...

rows.label: qst003103_msg0012
rows.name:
They'll probably end up having to
live here, so we need to try and calm
things down as much as possible.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0013
rows.name:
But thanks for all your help. I
feel like we have a chance now.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0014
rows.name:
We're short of meat-based meals
here. I'm counting on you!
